etomica.virial

Class ClusterWheatleyPartitionScreening

  • java.lang.Object
    • etomica.virial.ClusterWheatleyPartitionScreening
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ClusterAbstract, ClusterWheatley

    public class ClusterWheatleyPartitionScreening
extends java.lang.Object
implements ClusterWheatley
    This class calculates the sum of all biconnected clusters using Wheatley's recursive formulation.
